high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab the fork out of the sink
Move slightly to the right
Put the fork in the black mug in the sink
Grab the mug out of the sink
Turn right and stop at the counter
Put the mug on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a black mug with a fork in it on a counter

high_descs: Turn to the left and find the sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Carry the fork and look around.
Place the fork in the cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Carry the cup and move a step to the right.
Place the cup and fork on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and fork to the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the spatula that is in the sink.
With the spatula in hand turn so you are in front of the black cup in the sink.
Place the spatula in to the black cup that is in the sink.
Pick up the cup with the spatula in it that is in the sink.
Turn and go to the counter that is to the right of the sink with the cup and spatula in hand.
Place the cup with the spatula on to the counter to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place cup and spatula on counter.
